description.en:
Ebisu is EBS Network Token on BSC Market where you can buy and sell Ebisu Network if you like or use it to register copyright or own digital products. Besides, you can also join the exchanges that Ebisu Network has conveniently linked for trading and exchanging other types of Crypto.

In the long term, more people will want to own and invest in Ebisu Network because it is the leading platform in the world. We are ready to link with other digital markets for a future of product diversification from spirituality to material.
